transcript:
one quick strategy to help with your
anxiety next time you find yourself
feeling stressed or anxious ask yourself
this one question right now am I safe 99
of the time you are and this works
because when you're feeling anxious
you're almost always worried about the
future and your anxiety is a protection
and this question allows you to return
to the present moment and get your
nervous system to understand that right
now you're safe which will help you calm
down your nervous system and relieve
your anxiety
